1
00:00:03,980 --> 00:00:06,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">High school is no fun.</font>

2
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna go back to middle school.</font>

3
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:12,240
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#0c4b9a"><font size="20">MIDDLE SCHOOL
ALUMNI GATHERING</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:08,710 --> 00:00:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all you keep saying.</font>

5
00:00:11,670 --> 00:00:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing beats the old homestead.</font>

6
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one uses that word anymore, do they?</font>

7
00:00:14,870 --> 00:00:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your friends came with you 
to the culture festival, right?</font>

8
00:00:17,250 --> 00:00:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Individually, all my friends 
are good people.</font>

9
00:00:20,450 --> 00:00:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I just don't vibe with 
the overall feel of the school.</font>

10
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it gloomy?</font>

11
00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

12
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It always feels like there's 
this empty silence!</font>

13
00:00:26,930 --> 00:00:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there's an overwhelming 
lack of idiots.</font>

14
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are we supposed 
to take that statement?</font>

15
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mean academically. 
I mean the fun kind.</font>

16
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Third year of middle school after 
classes was the best, wasn't it?</font>

17
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the three of us—me, Yamada, and Miyu—
did that after-school study group.</font>

18
00:00:40,530 --> 00:00:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was seriously so much fun.</font>

19
00:00:41,020 --> 00:00:44,160
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#fdffa6"><font face="Trebuchet MS">AH HA HA</font></font></font></b></font>

20
00:00:41,020 --> 00:00:42,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#f9c0e5"><font face="Trebuchet MS">HEE HEE</font></font></font></b></font>

21
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean the one where we 
basically just talked, right?</font>

22
00:00:44,770 --> 00:00:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I remember is rolling with laughter 
at conversations with no substance.</font>

23
00:00:48,030 --> 00:00:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly! That's what I liked!</font>

24
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His vehemence is scary.</font>

25
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were students testing into high school,</font>

26
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we had no after-school activities, 
leaving us with such a sense of freedom!</font>

27
00:00:56,640 --> 00:01:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That rush of emotion from thinking, 
"Let's graduate without any regrets!"</font>

28
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The afternoon sun shining into 
the classroom... The melancholy feels...</font>

29
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's monologuing.</font>

30
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,170
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#82f8bc">POUT</font></font></b></font>

31
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although, Yamada got a girlfriend 
partway through and stopped coming.</font>

32
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real, right?</font>

33
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! That doesn't make me 
the bad guy here!</font>

34
00:01:11,090 --> 00:01:12,800
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">FLASHBACK TO
THE PREVIOUS EPISODE...</font></b></font>

35
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, around dusk,</font>

36
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for no reason, I'll take a walk down 
the route I took to middle school.</font>

37
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay?</font>

38
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I hear them singing choir 
songs we sang in middle school,</font>

39
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really feel like I'm about to cry.</font>

40
00:01:24,810 --> 00:01:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not okay.</font>

41
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you're having fun in the moment,</font>

42
00:01:28,340 --> 00:01:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you don't realize how lucky 
you are to be in that environment.</font>

43
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...is what Ricchan was saying.</font>

44
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like he must have it pretty rough.</font>

45
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

46
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just too hung up on the past!</font>

47
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's cold.</font>

48
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't empathisize with someone saying 
"middle school was too much fun."</i></font>

49
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And why was Suzuki attending 
this gathering like it was normal?</font>

50
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay with that, Tani?</font>

51
00:01:52,470 --> 00:01:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I think it's probably fine.</font>

52
00:01:56,290 --> 00:01:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And overthinking everything 
makes it seem like I don't trust her,</font>

53
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which feels disrespectful.</font>

54
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for being worried about us.</font>

55
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you getting more confident?</font>

56
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that bad?</font>

57
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Monster.</font>

58
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#094b71">DON'T LEAVE ME
BEHIND, TANI...</font></font></b></font>

59
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

60
00:02:23,410 --> 00:02:28,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial">YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES</font></b></font>

61
00:03:41,670 --> 00:03:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you getting?</font>

62
00:03:43,370 --> 00:03:45,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm in the mood for chicken curry.</font>

63
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Then I think I'll get 
the chicken hayashi.</font>

64
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that I think about it, 
there's this guy, too.</i></font>

65
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be headed toward 
falling in love right now!</font>

66
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What happened after that?</i></font>

67
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he make any progress?</i></font>

68
00:03:57,060 --> 00:04:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. I won't ask any questions 
until Yamada brings it up himself.</i></font>

69
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it didn't go well, 
I have nothing I can say to him.</i></font>

70
00:04:05,210 --> 00:04:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And even if it did go well, 
I still have nothing to say!</i></font>

71
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:09,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="12"><font face="Arial"><font color="#6effd8">(BECAUSE
I'D
FEEL
CONFLICTED
ABOUT
IT)</font></font></font></b></font>

72
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm just so...</i></font>

73
00:04:14,230 --> 00:04:18,150
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#153551"><font size="16">STAND-IN COMMENTATOR</font></font></b></font>

74
00:04:14,490 --> 00:04:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}On the day of the culture festival, 
this is what happened to Yamada!</font>

75
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this one you took?</font>

76
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

77
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Wow.</font>

78
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:29,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#10d3a1"><font face="Trebuchet MS">SILENCE . . .</font></font></b></font>

79
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

80
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm nervous again, 
so this conversation isn't...</i></font>

81
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I'm sorry my replies to the messages you 
sent over summer break were so awful."</i></font>

82
00:04:36,820 --> 00:04:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I'm sorry that it seemed like 
I was rejecting you."</i></font>

83
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I...</font>

84
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

85
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, go ahead!</font>

86
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

87
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

88
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For texting you... and everything else.</font>

89
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not close, wouldn't it be scary 
to suddenly be asked for contact info?</font>

90
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought maybe I've been too pushy.</font>

91
00:04:57,710 --> 00:05:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, given the distance 
between us and stuff.</font>

92
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll think a little more before I act.</font>

93
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

94
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishi-san, what were you going to say?</font>

95
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

96
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry too.</font>

97
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My phone... Up until now, 
I've used it to contact my parents,</font>

98
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and once in a while, I message Hon-chan</font>

99
00:05:17,970 --> 00:05:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or other girls I'm friends with, 
but that's all.</font>

100
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I overthink about whether 
I've written anything weird</font>

101
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or made typos, and it slows me down.</font>

102
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet, I still send 
ridiculously long texts.</font>

103
00:05:29,550 --> 00:05:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then I think too much about what 
would happen if I went silent on a call.</font>

104
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

105
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't that I didn't like it.</font>

106
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being scared of making mistakes 
makes me overthink everything.</font>

107
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be able 
to not overthink so much.</font>

108
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and I are polar opposites.</font>

109
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you sent something,</font>

110
00:05:51,710 --> 00:05:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it made me so happy that 
I'd reply right away without thinking.</font>

111
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought you wrote anything weird.</font>

112
00:05:57,130 --> 00:06:00,130
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#de5783">Thank goodness</font></font></b></font>

113
00:05:57,500 --> 00:06:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm nowhere near as concerned about 
details as you think I am, Nishi-san.</font>

114
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

115
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should just make mistakes! With me.</font>

116
00:06:06,370 --> 00:06:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

117
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:07,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#fbed78"><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS">WHAT?!</font></font></font></b></font>

118
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm not someone you need 
to be careful around at all.</font>

119
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're peers, right?</font>

120
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I'm being annoying, 
you can just say, "Ugh, what a pain!"</font>

121
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I'm making too much noise, 
you can just say, "Shut up, stupid!"</font>

122
00:06:17,650 --> 00:06:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't say that! Not that way.</font>

123
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"You're being entirely too loud."</font>

124
00:06:23,930 --> 00:06:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not that elegant.</font>

125
00:06:27,910 --> 00:06:30,160
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Arial"><font size="24">RIHITO</font></font></font></b></font>

126
00:06:27,910 --> 00:06:30,160
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">INCOMING CALL</font></font></font></b></font>

127
00:06:28,510 --> 00:06:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ricchan! I forgot!</font>

128
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna head out. Thanks!</font>

129
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay for me 
to talk to you at school?</font>

130
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

131
00:06:41,170 --> 00:06:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's talk again!</font>

132
00:06:43,100 --> 00:06:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And thus, they managed
 to make a little progress.</font>

133
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ever since the culture festival, 
he's been in an oddly good mood,</i></font>

134
00:06:52,610 --> 00:06:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and he's clearly been looking for 
someone while we've been here.</i></font>

135
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not gonna bite. I won't bite!</i></font>

136
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada-kun, are you looking for someone?</font>

137
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh.</font>

138
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gapacho.</font>

139
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not biting! You hear me?!</i></font>

140
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I won't think about it.</i></font>

141
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I mean...</i></font>

142
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Both Yamada and Tani 
are good guys to begin with.</i></font>

143
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,460
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="20">THINKING
ABOUT IT</font></font></b></font>

144
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of course there's someone who likes them, 
and they're able to accept that.</i></font>

145
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Taira-kun.</font>

146
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your personality's kinda different 
than I thought it was.</font>

147
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't remember stuff you hate.</i></font>

148
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What that friend of Yamada's said...</i></font>

149
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that middle school was so much 
fun and high school isn't.</i></font>

150
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Basically, it's a contrast thing.</i></font>

151
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not being able to choose your elementary 
or middle school makes them more hellish.</i></font>

152
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:48,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if he acknowledged that, 
from my perspective, I'd still be jealo—</i></font>

153
00:07:57,870 --> 00:08:00,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#ffffff">MOUTHING</font></font></b></font>

154
00:07:57,870 --> 00:07:58,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#24b8af"><font size="24">FLAP</font></font></font></b></font>

155
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:58,620
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#24b8af"><font size="24">FLAP</font></font></font></b></font>

156
00:07:58,620 --> 00:07:59,000
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#24b8af"><font size="24">FLAP</font></font></font></b></font>

157
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,370
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#24b8af"><font size="24">FLAP</font></font></font></b></font>

158
00:07:59,090 --> 00:08:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't saying anything?</font>

159
00:07:59,370 --> 00:07:59,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#24b8af"><font size="24">FLAP</font></font></font></b></font>

