00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hon-chan!</font>

218
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

219
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

220
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Morning.</font>

221
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that face?</font>

222
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In spite of everything, 
you seem to be getting along well!</font>

223
00:09:58,730 --> 00:10:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Nisshi...</font>

224
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what do you think of Yamada so far?</font>

225
00:10:02,050 --> 00:10:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

226
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My heart pounds.</font>

227
00:10:08,430 --> 00:10:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

228
00:10:10,350 --> 00:10:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what?</font>

229
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know how to put it...</font>

230
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what this feeling could be.</font>

231
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:19,310
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="48">{\an8}<font color="#ffffc5">BA-DUMP...</font></font></font></b></font>

232
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what this feeling could be.</font>

233
00:10:19,810 --> 00:10:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There are people in real life 
who actually say that!</i></font>

234
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:22,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#45ffd7">I'VE SEEN IT...
