235
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean like, "I wonder what this 
tingling in the depths of my chest is"?</font>

236
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. It's nothing so fancy.</font>

237
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not fancy.</font>

238
00:10:32,650 --> 00:10:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if it's Yamada-kun or the 
situation that is making my heart pound.</font>

239
00:10:37,660 --> 00:10:40,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#ec8b08">Urk....</font></font></b></font>

240
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. That's a lot more realistic 
than I thought it would be.</font>

241
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My experience in talking with 
boys is so drastically lacking that</font>

242
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my heart pounds really hard and it's 
difficult to know why it's pounding.</font>

243
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it wasn't Yamada-kun, I think 
my heart would still pound like that.</font>

244
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dear, dear. I see.</font>

245
00:10:53,170 --> 00:10:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I'm relieved to know that 
you aren't too dense a heroine.</font>

246
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Don't mind me.</font>

247
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, even if the situation is what 
has you going, that's not an issue, is it?</font>

248
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But... doesn't that make it 
seem like anyone would do?</font>

249
00:11:09,950 --> 00:11:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's no point in 
thinking about that, is there?</font>

250
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

251
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Basically, in the case that your heart is 
pounding because of the situation,</font>

252
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the question of whether your heart would 
pound if it was someone other than Yamada</font>

253
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is what you get hung up on, right?</font>

254
00:11:23,210 --> 00:11:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is.</font>

255
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nisshi, at the present moment, 
do you have this "someone else"?</font>

256
00:11:27,950 --> 00:11:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I don't.</font>

257
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, aren't you comparing Yamada 
to something that doesn't exist?</font>

258
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"But what if things were like this..."</font>

259
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a worry that you 
created out of nothing,</font>

260
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you can create 
those infinitely, right?</font>

261
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to be bothered by 
something, better reality than what-ifs.</font>

262
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be better to go with a simple,
 "How do I feel about this person?"</font>

263
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see. That's true.</font>

264
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, first, I need to be able 
to talk without getting nervous.</font>

265
00:11:53,390 --> 00:11:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, that's always the thing.</font>

266
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font face="Trebuchet MS">BACK TO THE START AGAIN</font></font></b></font>

