00:11:55,570 --> 00:11:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heave-ho!</font>

268
00:11:56,990 --> 00:12:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry! Whether it's a boy or 
a girl, in the end, everyone's human.</font>

269
00:12:01,490 --> 00:12:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hon-chan is kind of scary sometimes.</i></font>

270
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll get used to it over time.</font>

271
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And whether your heart's pounding 
