276
00:12:25,470 --> 00:12:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not even not being shy.</font>

277
00:12:28,210 --> 00:12:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regardless of gender, I basically 
